				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">OoW first thoughts -xping<a name="62056"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 15 04 10:16 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, I didn't really get a chance to explore the new zones, but I did want to ding and get a decent amount of xp into 66.  So I got a group together in Earth and good lord...I killed 100+ mobs for about 20% xp.  Looks like our 66-70 levels may be brand new h*ll levels.
<br />

<br />
What's the xp like in the other zones? I was thinking about going to KT, I was told the xp there was a <i>little</i> better. Oh and a druid on Prexus is already 68 at this writing..d*mn dr00ds!
<br />
</span></td>
