				<td colspan="2"><span>I explored a bit, to proving grounds, tried a trial.
<br />

<br />
XP is not that great in the zones that I went too so far, so I went back to KT (39 people there, wtf?).  Eventually endded up in Yxxta and xp was ok.
<br />

<br />
IMO, Walls of Slaughter has advantages for bards and for monks.  Monks becuase not lullable so far (although very few were tightly packed), very large agro range and see invis nameds.  Bards becuase they run super fast.
<br />

<br />
Anyways, I'm having fun.</span></td>
